Articles.Content:
Whatever Will Be, Will Be :-)

I want to send probe with press-meter into polar orbit, make measures in low Kerbin Orbit and High Kerbin Orbit fulfilling polar orbit contact at the same time, than to de-orbit and make measurement on upper atmosphere layer and lower layer than land on Parachute, but the life is thought i don't managed to reach desired orbit and forget the chute :-(

I not plan well this mission i hoped that if part of experiments i developed for this mission will be performed this mission will be successful at least in scientific terms

So as the words of the song Que Sera Sera "Whatever Will Be, Will Be"
